::Epyon::

"Arggg! This Angel Prime is correct! Never surrender! Fight till you
cant fight anymore!"

::Hot Rod::

He heard the comm chatter. He hadn't recieved a response from IR so he
was going through with this mission under orders or not. He also saw
that Angel Prime wasn't comeing, so he opened a comm to Angel Prime.
"Now isn't the time to arue, Angel, but I agree. I need your help, with
the Matrix. We're going to save Optimus Prime!"
He reached Dark Prime's position.
"Hot Rod, maximize."
He transformed to bot mode.
"Hello Optimus..."
